description: High Fusion Inc. focuses on developing and manufacturing branded products in the cannabis industry with a specific focus on flower, pro-rolls, vapes, edibles, and oil extracts for medical and adult recreational use in the United States. Its brand portfolio includes FLÏ edibles and vape product, OutCo, and Thrive brands. The company was formerly known as Nutritional High International Inc. and changed its name to High Fusion Inc. in November 2021. High Fusion Inc. was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
